            <pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 06:22:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1201433</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本著名的電子遊戲製作商 Konami 於「Xbox 合作夥伴預覽（Xbox Partner Peview）」展示會上，公佈了早前宣佈重製的遊戲《Metal Gear Solid Delta: Snake Eater》（潛龍諜影 Delta：食蛇者）的新預告片，片中寫實精美的畫面由最新一代 Unreal Engine 5 遊戲引擎重新展示。</p><p>Konami 在遊戲預告片中展示了過去潛龍系列中的標誌性玩法，而主角「Snake」將隻身空降深入危險的熱帶叢林與山嶽地帶。面對嚴酷險惡的自然環境，以及虎視眈眈的動物與敵人，一邊求生、一邊任務。</p><p>影片的結尾更確認實機遊戲畫面由最新一代 Unreal Engine 5 遊戲引擎重新製作。其中展示的多個遊戲環境和動物，例如在草地上滑行的蛇、水裏的蟹、用手槍攻擊對方的畫面都相當精美。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="size-medium wp-image-1201438 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.16.54-694x367.png" alt="" width="694" height="367" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.16.54-694x367.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.16.54-1280x677.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.16.54-768x406.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.16.54.png 1520w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1201439 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.17.04-694x359.png" alt="" width="694" height="359" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.17.04-694x359.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.17.04-1280x662.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.17.04-768x397.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.17.04.png 1508w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1201440 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.17.53-694x367.png" alt="" width="694" height="367" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-26-12.17.53-